name: The General Fuzz
details:
The General Germanium FuzzDelivers the warm, vintage fuzz tones of a late 60s’-era germanium transistor-based pedal
Covers a range of retro fuzz sounds, from darker, more sustained/compressed sounds to more subtle, Texas Blues-sounding dirt 
Responsive to your guitar’s volume level: dial back your volume knob for a cleaner sound whose bite is a little more understated
